quantitative and qualitative disclosures about market risk the company engages in activities that expose it to various market risks  including the effects of changes in foreign currency exchange rates  interest rates and natural gas prices 
the financial exposure is managed as an integral part of the company s risk management program  which seeks to reduce the potentially adverse effects that the volatility of the markets may have on operating results 
